{"tid":2334671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國頭號通緝殺人犯藏身香港","createTime":"2020-12-21T10:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T15:55:45.000Z","uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"249420f0e2c8d205302e4cfaa392a5a395aa14d3","tid":2334671,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"法國警方相信，法國一名頭號通緝犯正藏身香港，並「百分之九十九肯定」他會再犯嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n英國天空電視引述法國警方說，這名叫瓦利的通緝犯，患有抑鬱、偏執和精神分裂，任何遇到他的人都有危險，希望公眾充分意識這一點。<br />\n<br />\n瓦利涉嫌2011年，在法國東部一處機場控制搭，用斧頭殺死一名同事。警方相信，瓦利案發後逃往瑞士，修改護照上的姓氏，再經澳門逃往香港。他其後被發現偽造護照和非法入境被捕，2014年一度服刑，2016年失去蹤影，2018年法國警方接獲線報，指他仍然在香港，現時無進一步證據顯示他已離境。"},{"pid":"cf5fde4097fb9c6fc59cc805a1e73a20a3bec491","tid":2334671,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566424-20201221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566424-20201221.htm&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=e9a9791d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566424-20201221.htm&h=d64058e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566424-20201221.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11a766e34404e0ce54c40d69521b7496b37886d5","tid":2334671,"uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"洋腸港女驚唔驚？<br />\n一陣含中左碌殺人腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce9390039bda66810420666849f2917b805e273","tid":2334671,"uid":300262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11a766e34404e0ce54c40d69521b7496b37886d5","tid":2334671,"uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"洋腸港女驚唔驚？<br />\n一陣含中左碌殺人腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm